{"tid":1449454,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"今晚柏麗大道嘅手足 入一入嚟","createTime":"2019-08-11T16:54:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T06:22:21.000Z","uid":147376,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e328d220b8c7365797c6fce4b4aef433bdd8bdfe","tid":1449454,"uid":147376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:54:59.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">其實畜龍突發跑出嚟捉人嘅十分鐘前，已經有大量資訊話會清場，包圍</span><br />\n<br />\n<strong>有少數清醒嘅現場手足嘗試係速龍清場前十幾分鐘叫人留意，包括旺角方向有大量狗車嚟緊尖沙咀，叫人準備要退，但結果呢？結果畀人話係鬼，散水撚呀！</strong><br />\n<br />\n至少10個手足被捕，本來係可以避免<br />\n<br />\n<strong>前線或者每一個現場手足，<span style=\"color: red;\">可唔可以保持警覺</span>，用tg又好，連登又好，fb/youtube live都好，<span style=\"color: red;\">留意吓身邊發生緊嘅事(例如狗車數量，前往方向，狗擺陣變動)，然後最重要！現場大嗌出嚟呀！</span>前線聽唔到就要嗌大聲啲，或者搵人傳話，同時用吓你嘅獨立思考，諗吓危唔危險，幾時進，幾時撤</strong><br />\n<br />\n收到任何資訊都要向當時人fact check再考慮撤定唔撤，而唔係第一句就話人散水撚，係鬼！<br />\n<br />\n呢個post唔係譴責，唔係割蓆，而係最後嘅提醒<br />\n<br />\n革命係漫漫長路，唔好貪一時之氣，畀仇恨蒙蔽雙眼，因為你睇到嘅，只係眼前嘅狗屋同狗，你可以知道幾條街外有畜龍嚟緊捉你嗎？相信你嘅手足，今日散，他日可以再聚<br />\n<br />\n保持警覺，理性抗爭，退唔代表輸，成功亦唔係用死一個方法就可以達到<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申睇住尖沙咀前線「直播」<br />\n明嘅就自然明</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/x3bHhdv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fx3bHhdv.jpg&h=37599e4c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qxrW56W.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqxrW56W.jpg&h=d7cf9435&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ceZJL60.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FceZJL60.jpg&h=0815896a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EjR0Oko.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEjR0Oko.jpg&h=e46eeff0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">最後 1940 畜龍衝出嚟捉咗10個手足<br />\n而早係1930，即十分鐘前已經有手足知道唔妥叫人注意同走</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4QRzSNg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4QRzSNg.jpg&h=6148131b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fe49a0665b59db845a6a391bee17c9b8a40c35c8","tid":1449454,"uid":147376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:55:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7d8118ba8c3dbdb697610f48c55092aef53f4168","tid":1449454,"uid":147376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:56:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fbd02f1a8b31b2d3d1c23112bc8e55eb05afdcf4","tid":1449454,"uid":90881,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:58:09.000Z","msg":"好多時前線根本收唔到信號"},{"pid":"acc7066e93b7b569b617480ba9028e9ecca53927","tid":1449454,"uid":158977,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:59:26.000Z","msg":"前線冇任何資訊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我乜撚野都唔知呀屌鳩你"},{"pid":"8e522b9b0f15ab9ad5ac89bcbeb53402261d3fe1","tid":1449454,"uid":147376,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:00:13.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>前線手足：多聽意見，資訊，勿戀戰<br />\n中間手足：多睇資訊，大聲嗌資訊，用腦判斷，傳話傳資訊畀前線<br />\n後面手足：多睇資訊，大聲嗌資訊，用腦判斷，傳話傳資訊畀中間手足，企疏少少，以便逃走<br />\n<br />\n全部手足：保持警覺，由多方面渠道留意消息(tg,連登,youtube,fb)<br />\n<br />\n</strong></span>"},{"pid":"e1a8da77836c3b2e161aa67f28a64c5ff2fb85fe","tid":1449454,"uid":147376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fbd02f1a8b31b2d3d1c23112bc8e55eb05afdcf4","tid":1449454,"uid":90881,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:58:09.000Z","msg":"好多時前線根本收唔到信號"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:02:04.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>而家係後面，中間嘅手足收到資訊(狗包圍緊，有大量狗車增援)但你哋前線唔肯撤，唔肯信，仲屌返人地<br />\n<br />\n10分鐘後速龍突然衝出嚟清場，至少10個手足被拉</strong></span>"},{"pid":"797ef7dfec5fb91b38a87fc15165bb4bfacb31d6","tid":1449454,"uid":147376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:03:26.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">不譴責 不割席 不篤灰<br />\n<br />\n真心提醒<br />\n<br />\n再咁落去真係會散<br />\n<br />\n理智係抗爭嘅最好工具</span>"},{"pid":"f0705291d242482e94c457df21159b2026d225e3","tid":1449454,"uid":147376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:03:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4450c576bb222f8a313c93bbee5b3cce9b90ad3c","tid":1449454,"uid":147376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:03:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"eebe771df08f4d23d40ff56e811c91d81be772c4","tid":1449454,"uid":147376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:05:31.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">有10個手足畀人拉，有個女仔畀狗射盲咗，我當堂喊到收唔到聲崩潰呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"dca4d0f98f9e6907ad54e8e065f60d6bc2cf8d61","tid":1449454,"uid":147376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:05:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a31c1bc5cfefcbc5cb8e64bcba5d0197afd52f7b","tid":1449454,"uid":147376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:06:07.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">唔好再送頭啦，好嗎？</span>"},{"pid":"8a93abb3a94e6231dde421b47ffe48ab048433af","tid":1449454,"uid":147376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:06:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fb8a110c41ecc7c74f1648a6d8fa1ffd848acb47","tid":1449454,"uid":147376,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:07:59.000Z","msg":"我講過類似嘅嘢，點解冇人睇?<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1402108\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1402108</a>"},{"pid":"ed4cbf734b979444dd0e7278ceb63fa277bd66ec","tid":1449454,"uid":147376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:09:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0e676be3c3c5a7e31100dd83ecd6a93fb2528c87","tid":1449454,"uid":147376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:09:33.000Z","ms